---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AffiliateLink from '../components/AffiliateLink.astro';

const meta = {
  title: 'Durable AI Review: I Built a Site in 30 Seconds (2025)',
  description: 'Honest Durable AI review after actually using it. Fast website generation, but limited customization and you\'re locked into their platform.',
  image: '/og-image.svg',
  keywords: ['Durable AI review', 'Durable AI website builder', 'Durable.co honest review', 'AI website generator', 'Durable vs alternatives'],
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-[#FEF9F3] py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-black text-[#E07A5F] mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
        Tested · Honest · No Hype
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        Durable AI Review: I Built a Site in 30 Seconds
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Durable AI generates complete websites in seconds. It's fast, impressive, but has real limitations. Here's what you need to know before paying.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-[#E07A5F]/10 border-2 border-[#E07A5F] rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quick verdict: Durable is best for quick MVPs and simple business sites. Not for serious projects or anything requiring customization. You're trading control for speed. Worth it for testing ideas. Not worth it for long-term assets.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Durable Does -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Durable AI Actually Does
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 my-8">
      <p class="text-lg font-black mb-4">You enter your business name and industry. Durable generates:</p>

      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li>• Complete website (homepage + multiple sections)</li>
        <li>• Copy written for your specific business</li>
        <li>• Images selected (AI-generated or stock)</li>
        <li>• Contact forms and scheduling</li>
        <li>• Mobile-responsive design</li>
        <li>• SEO basics (meta tags, structure)</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">Time from "tell me about your business" to live site: Under 1 minute. Actually impressive technology.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-[#E07A5F]/10 border-2 border-[#E07A5F] rounded-xl p-6">
      <p class="font-bold mb-2">The catch:</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">You're locked into Durable's platform. Exporting isn't really an option. Customization is limited. The generated content is generic "AI business" copy that needs human rewriting. You're trading ownership for speed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Durable Pricing (January 2025)
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- Starter -->
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-xl text-gray-900">Starter (Monthly)</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">For testing and simple sites</p>
          </div>
          <span class="bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">$15/mo</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>✓ 1 website</li>
          <li>✓ Free subdomain (your-site.durable.co)</li>
          <li>✓ AI generation</li>
          <li>✓ Basic customization</li>
          <li>✓ SSL certificate</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://durable.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-black py-3 px-6 rounded-lg">
          Start Free Trial
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Business -->
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-xl text-gray-900">Business (Monthly)</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">For growing businesses</p>
          </div>
          <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">$25/mo</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>✓ 3 websites</li>
          <li>✓ Custom domain</li>
          <li>✓ AI blog writer</li>
          <li>✓ Invoicing</li>
          <li>✓ CRM tools</li>
          <li>✓ Priority support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://durable.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-black py-3 px-6 rounded-lg">
          Get Business
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Mojo Growth -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-xl text-gray-900">Mojo Growth (Yearly)</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">All features + AI marketing tools</p>
          </div>
          <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">$30/mo</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>✓ Everything in Business</li>
          <li>✓ Unlimited websites</li>
          <li>✓ AI ad generator</li>
          <li>✓ SEO tools</li>
          <li>✓ Analytics</li>
          <li>✓ White label option</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://durable.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-black py-3 px-6 rounded-lg">
          Get Mojo Growth
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I Liked -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Durable Does Well
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✓ Actually Fast</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Not marketing fast. Real fast. Enter "coffee shop Brooklyn" → 30 seconds later → complete website with menu, location, contact form, About section. The speed is genuinely impressive for what you get.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Most "AI website builders" are slow wrappers around ChatGPT. Durable feels like actual tech built for this specific purpose.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✓ Business-Specific Output</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Durable asks smart questions about your business. Location, services, target customer. The generated site reflects this. A plumber's site looks different from a consultant's site.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Compare to generic "business website" templates that don't adapt to your industry.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✓ Complete, Not Just Landing Page</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You get homepage, services, about, contact. Multiple sections. It's a real multi-page website (or single-page with sections). Not just a hero section and CTA.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Enough structure to actually launch a simple business presence.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✓ Built-in Business Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Higher tiers include invoicing, CRM, scheduling. These integrate with your site. Not just website builder—mini business operating system.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Legitimately useful for solo businesses who want everything in one place.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✓ No Technical Skill Needed</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Truly zero-code. No drag-and-drop learning curve. Answer questions → get website. Your non-technical aunt could use this.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Accessibility is the real selling point. Not for us (technical people). For everyone else.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Sucks -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Doesn't Work (Dealbreakers)
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✗ Locked-In Platform</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You cannot export your site. Period. Durable sites live on Durable. If you leave, you rebuild from scratch.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">This is the biggest limitation. You're renting your website, not owning it. Fine for MVP, terrible for long-term asset.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✗ Limited Customization</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You can change colors, fonts, images, copy. But you're working within Durable's templates. Want a custom layout? Want different sections? Want unique design?</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Not possible. You pick from what Durable offers. All Durable sites have that "Durable look."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✗ Generic AI Copy</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The writing is grammatically correct and relevant. But it's generic. "We're committed to excellence" type filler. You WILL want to rewrite everything.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Durable gives you structure. You provide the personality. If you don't customize the copy, your site sounds like every other AI-generated site.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✗ No Advanced Features</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Need a blog? Limited. Need e-commerce? Not really there. Need custom integrations? Good luck. Need database-driven features? Forget it.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Durable is for brochure sites. Simple business presence. That's the envelope. Don't push it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✗ Monthly Subscription Forever</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Stop paying? Lose your site. Unlike buying a domain and building with <AffiliateLink href="https://wordpress.org">WordPress</AffiliateLink> or <AffiliateLink href="https://vercel.com">Vercel</AffiliateLink> (one-time work, minimal ongoing cost), Durable is endless monthly fee.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">$15-30/month forever = $180-360/year. For a simple site? Adds up.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- When to Use Durable -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      When Durable Is Worth It (And When It's Not)
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✅ Use Durable if:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• You need a site TODAY and have zero technical skills</li>
          <li>• Testing a business idea (MVP)</li>
          <li>• Simple local business (plumber, salon, restaurant)</li>
          <li>• Freelancer who needs basic web presence fast</li>
          <li>• You don't care about owning the code/design</li>
          <li>• Budget $15-30/month is fine for ongoing cost</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">❌ Don't use Durable if:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• You want to own your website (can't export)</li>
          <li>• You need custom design or features</li>
          <li>• Building a serious long-term asset</li>
          <li>• You have some technical skill or can hire someone</li>
          <li>• You want scalability (growing beyond basic site)</li>
          <li>• Ongoing monthly fees bother you</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Better Alternative -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      The Middle Ground: Use Durable as Prototype
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 my-8">
      <p class="text-lg font-black mb-4">Smart workflow: Durable for prototyping, rebuild properly for production.</p>

      <ol class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Use Durable to generate your site in 30 seconds</li>
        <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Customize the copy to sound like you (not AI)</li>
        <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Test the layout, structure, what works</li>
        <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> If business validates, rebuild properly with <AffiliateLink href="https://wordpress.org">WordPress</AffiliateLink>, <AffiliateLink href="https://webflow.com">Webflow</AffiliateLink>, or custom code</li>
        <li><strong>Step 5:</strong> Migrate your custom content (the only thing that mattered)</li>
      </ol>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-6">You get Durable's speed for ideation. You get ownership for long-term. Best of both worlds.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Durable vs Alternatives
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="p-4 border font-bold">Feature</th>
            <th class="p-4 border font-bold">Durable</th>
            <th class="p-4 border font-bold">v0.dev</th>
            <th class="p-4 border font-bold"><a href="/framer-vs-durable" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Framer</a></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border">Speed</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">⚡⚡⚡ Fastest</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">⚡⚡ Fast</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">⚡ Medium</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 border">Code ownership</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">❌ No</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">✓ Yes</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Partial</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border">Customization</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Limited</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Full</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">High</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 border">Technical skill</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">None</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Medium</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Low-Medium</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border">Best for</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Quick MVPs</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Developers</td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Designers</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom Line -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="bg-[#E07A5F]/10 border-2 border-[#E07A5F] rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-6">The Bottom Line</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Durable AI is impressive technology that solves the "I need a website fast" problem. It genuinely delivers on its promise: complete site in under a minute.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">But the limitations are real. You're locked in. Customization is limited. You don't own what you build.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Use cases:</p>

      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li>• <strong>MVP testing</strong> — Validate idea with real site fast</li>
        <li>• <strong>Simple business</strong> — Local services that just need basic presence</li>
        <li>• <strong>Non-technical users</strong> — People who can't/won't use traditional builders</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Avoid for:</p>

      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li>• <strong>Long-term assets</strong> — Build properly if this matters</li>
        <li>• <strong>Custom needs</strong> — Durable can't flex beyond templates</li>
        <li>• <strong>Ownership matters</strong> — You can't take it with you</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">The smart approach: Use Durable to prototype fast. If the business validates, rebuild properly. You get speed now without sacrificing ownership later.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-gray-900">
      Related AI Builder Guides
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/durable-vs-v0-vs-framer" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Durable vs v0 vs Framer</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Top AI builders compared</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/ai-website-hosting" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI Website Hosting Guide</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">What you need to know</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
